				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Here is me bit o input on halfling druids. I am a level 22 halfling druid on the Xegony server. I find that we halflings make the best fightin druids, ... we can club stuff to death better when short on mana. If you want a more magical druid, stick with a wood elf, or focus yer points on wisdom. I started my druid with 85 str points, added a few to stamina, and only 5 to wisdom, making it 95. With some +wis jewelry and trinkets, I made it 106, and I am doing fine. VERY soloable so far, and fun!<BR>
<BR>
-Rootric Bazillion, ==Flying Halflings==
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
	<tr>
