			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Sorry if you dis-agree but I think halflings are the best at whatt they can be. They make the best Druids and the best Rogues, havnt played halfing cleric tho. Warrior halfling isnt too bad of a choice either cuz they so fast, although their arent too many halfling warriors over lvl 20. I have a lvl 30 halfling rogue and I am kicking ass. This is a must character for all you newbies to ever quest. Only bad thing is the low charisma, whcih isnt too much of a big deal if your a rogue because people dont like ya too mcuh anyways. A great thing for all halfings is sneak and hide. When merchants wont buy/sell to you get behind them and hit sneak, then they will buy/sell. Just besure to hit sneak instead of back stab, that can be bad, trust me :o)<BR>
<BR>
Billymojo Stabbomo &lt;The Norrathian Protectorate&gt;<BR>
Bertox server
